Package ohos.agp.database

Class DataSetSubscriber

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.agp.database.DataSetSubscriber

  • public abstract class DataSetSubscriber
extends Object
    An abstract class that defines the behavior to be observed.

    This class defines the data behavior that an subscriber needs to observe, such as data changes and invalidated data. You can override the methods in this class to make responses to the data changes.
